\lang1033\ldblquote Still \'85 the prudent wizard keeps his head down in such times. All very well for Dumbledore to talk, but taking up a post at Hog\-warts just now would be tantamount to declaring my public alle\-giance to the Order of the Phoenix! And while I\rquote m sure they\rquote re very admirable and brave and all the rest of it, I don\rquote t personally fancy the mortality rate \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
