\lang1033\ldblquote He and Professor Trelawney are dividing classes between them this year,\rdblquote  said Professor McGonagall, a hint of disapproval in her voice; it was common knowledge that she despised the subject of Divination. \ldblquote The sixth year is being taken by Professor Trelawney.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Parvati set off for Divination five minutes later looking slightly crestfallen.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote So, Potter, Potter \'85\rdblquote  said Professor McGonagall, consulting her notes as she turned to Harry. \ldblquote Charms, Defense Against the Dark Arts, Herbology, Transfiguration \'85 all fine. I must say, I was pleased with your Transfiguration mark, Potter, very pleased. Now, why haven\rquote t you applied to continue with Potions? I thought it was your ambition to become an Auror?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
