\lang1033 A few minutes later, Ron was cleared to do the same subjects as Harry, and the two of them left the table together.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Look,\rdblquote  said Ron delightedly, gazing at his schedule, \ldblquote we\rquote ve got a free period now\lang3081  \lang1033\'85 and a free period after break \'85 and after lunch \'85 \i excellent\i0 !\rdblquote\lang3081\par
