\lang1033\ldblquote Your defenses,\rdblquote  said Snape, a little louder, \ldblquote must therefore be as flexible and inventive as the arts you seek to undo. These pictures\rdblquote  \emdash  he indicated a few of them as he swept past \emdash  \ldblquote give a fair rep\-resentation of what happens to those who suffer, for instance, the Cruciatus Curse\rdblquote  \emdash  he waved a hand toward a witch who was clearly shrieking in agony \emdash  \ldblquote feel the Dementor\rquote s Kiss\rdblquote  \emdash  a wiz\-ard lying huddled and blank-eyed, slumped against a wall \emdash  \ldblquote or provoke the aggression of the Inferius\rdblquote  \emdash  a bloody mass upon the ground.\lang3081\par
