\lang1033 He set off again around the other side of the classroom toward his desk, and again, they watched him as he walked, his dark robes billowing behind him.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\'85 you are, I believe, complete novices in the use of nonverbal spells. What is the advantage of a nonverbal spell?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Hermione\rquote s hand shot into the air. Snape took his time looking around at everybody else, making sure he had no choice, before saying curtly, \ldblquote Very well \emdash  Miss Granger?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
