\lang1033\ldblquote Good lord, you\rquote re right!\rdblquote  said the man\rquote s voice. \ldblquote That\rquote ll be the son, I told you he\rquote s not right in the head. Don\rquote t look at it, Cecilia, darling.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 The jingling and clopping sounds were now growing fainter again.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote  \lquote\i Darling,\i0\rquote  \rdblquote  whispered Morfin in Parseltongue, looking at his sister. \ldblquote  \lquote\i Darling,\i0\rquote\i  he called her. So he wouldn\rquote t have you anyway.\i0\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Merope was so white Harry felt sure she was going to faint.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i What\rquote s that\i0 ?\rdblquote  said Gaunt sharply, also in Parseltongue, looking from his son to his daughter. \ldblquote\i What did you say, Morfin\i0 ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i She likes looking at that Muggle,\i0\rdblquote  said Morfin, a vicious expres\-sion on his face as he stared at his sister, who now looked terrified. \ldblquote\i Always in the garden when he passes, peering through the hedge at him, isn\rquote t she? And last night\lang3081\i0  \lang1033\emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Merope shook her head jerkily, imploringly, but Morfin went on ruthlessly, \ldblquote\i Hanging out of the window waiting for him to ride home, wasn\rquote t she\i0 ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Hanging out of the window to look at a Muggle\i0 ?\rdblquote  said Gaunt quietly.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 All three of the Gaunts seemed to have forgotten Ogden, who was looking both bewildered and irritated at this renewed outbreak of incomprehensible hissing and rasping.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\i Is it true\i0 ?\rdblquote\lang3081  \lang1033 said Gaunt in a deadly voice, advancing a step or two toward the terrified girl. \ldblquote\i My daughter\lang3081  \lang1033\i0\emdash\lang3081  \lang1033\i pure-blooded descendant of\lang3081  \lang1033 Salazar Slytherin \i0\emdash  \i hankering after a filthy, dirt-veined Muggle\i0 ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Merope shook her head frantically, pressing herself into the wall, apparently unable to speak.\lang3081\par
