\lang1033\ldblquote And it\lang3081  \lang1033\'85 it\rquote s got something to do with the prophecy?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote It has everything to do with the prophecy.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Right,\rdblquote  said Harry, a little confused, but reassured all the same.\lang3081\par
