\lang1033 Riddle nodded. Dumbledore got to his feet and held out his hand again. Taking it, Riddle said, \ldblquote I can speak to snakes. I found out when we\rquote ve been to the country on trips \emdash  they find me, they whisper to me. Is that normal for a wizard?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
