\ldblquote Wow, scary thought, the boy You-Know-Who,\rdblquote  said Ron qui\-etly, as they took their places around one of the gnarled Snargaluff stumps that formed this term\rquote s project, and began pulling on their protective gloves. \ldblquote But I still don\rquote t get why Dumbledore\rquote s showing you all this. I mean, it\rquote s really interesting and everything, but what\rquote s the point?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
