\lang1033\ldblquote Right,\rdblquote  said Ginny, tossing her long red hair out of her face and glaring at Ron, \ldblquote let\rquote s get this straight once and for all. It is none of your business who I go out with or what I do with them, Ron \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
