\lang1033\ldblquote Oh yes he does!\rdblquote  she said, flaring up at Harry. \ldblquote Just because \i he\rquote s\i0  never snogged anyone in his life, just because the best kiss \i he\rquote s\i0  ever had is from our Auntie Muriel \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
