\lang1033 Hermione gave him the kind of nasty look she had just given his copy of \i Advanced Potion-Making.\lang3081\i0\par
\lang1033\ldblquote It was all on the back of the bottles they showed Ginny and me in the summer,\rdblquote  she said coldly. \ldblquote I don\rquote t go around putting potions in people\rquote s drinks \'85 or pretending to, either, which is just as bad. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, well, never mind that,\rdblquote  said Harry quickly. \ldblquote The point is, Filch is being fooled, isn\rquote t he? These girls are getting stuff into the school disguised as something else! So why couldn\rquote t Malfoy have brought the necklace into the school \emdash  ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Oh, Harry \'85 not that again \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
