\lang1033\ldblquote But meanwhile,\rdblquote  said George, sitting down at the kitchen table and putting his feet up on it, \ldblquote we can enjoy watching you demon\-strate the correct use of a \emdash  whoops-a-daisy!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
