\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m sure you\rquote ll dazzle us all with hitherto unsuspected magical skills,\rdblquote  yawned Fred.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote And speaking of hitherto unsuspected skills, Ronald,\rdblquote  said George, \ldblquote what is this we hear from Ginny about you and a young lady called \emdash  unless our information is faulty \emdash  Lavender Brown?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Ron turned a little pink, but did not look displeased as he turned back to the sprouts. \ldblquote Mind your own business.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What a snappy retort,\rdblquote  said Fred. \ldblquote I really don\rquote t know how you think of them. No, what we wanted to know was \'85 how did it happen?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What d\rquote you mean?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
