\lang1033\ldblquote But we\rquote ve been away, how\rquote re we supposed to \emdash  ?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Harry! Ginny!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Hermione was hurrying toward them, very pink-faced and wear\-ing a cloak, hat, and gloves.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I got back a couple of hours ago, I\rquote ve just been down to visit Hagrid and Buck \emdash  I mean Witherwings,\rdblquote  she said breathlessly. \ldblquote Did you have a good Christmas?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah,\rdblquote  said Ron at once, \ldblquote pretty eventful, Rufus Scrim \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote ve got something for you, Harry,\rdblquote  said Hermione, neither looking at Ron nor giving any sign that she had heard him. \ldblquote Oh, hang on \emdash  password. \i Abstinence.\i0\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Precisely,\rdblquote  said the Fat Lady in a feeble voice, and swung for\-ward to reveal the portrait hole.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote What\rquote s up with her?\rdblquote  asked Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Overindulged over Christmas, apparently,\rdblquote  said Hermione, rolling her eyes as she led the way into the packed common room. \ldblquote She and her friend Violet drank their way through all the wine in that picture of drunk monks down by the Charms corridor. Anyway \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 She rummaged in her pocket for a moment, then pulled out a scroll of parchment with Dumbledore\rquote s writing on it.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Great,\rdblquote  said Harry, unrolling it at once to discover that his next lesson with Dumbledore was scheduled for the following night. \ldblquote I\rquote ve got loads to tell him \emdash  and you. Let\rquote s sit down \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 But at that moment there was a loud squeal of \ldblquote Won-Won!\rdblquote  and Lavender Brown came hurtling out of nowhere and flung herself into Ron\rquote s arms. Several onlookers sniggered; Hermione gave a\lang3081  \lang1033 tinkling laugh and said, \ldblquote There\rquote s a table over here. \'85 Coming, Ginny?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote No, thanks, I said I\rquote d meet Dean,\rdblquote  said Ginny, though Harry could not help noticing that she did not sound very enthusiastic. Leaving Ron and Lavender locked in a kind of vertical wrestling match, Harry led Hermione over to the spare table.\lang3081\par
