\lang1033\ldblquote The \i Prophet\i0  is bound to report the truth occasionally,\rdblquote  said Dumbledore, \ldblquote if only accidentally. Yes, that was why we argued. Well, it appears that Rufus found a way to corner you at last.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
