\lang1033 Dumbledore opened his mouth to speak and then closed it again. Behind Harry, Fawkes the phoenix let out a low, soft, musi\-cal cry. To Harry\rquote s intense embarrassment, he suddenly realized\lang3081  \lang1033 that Dumbledore\rquote s bright blue eyes looked rather watery, and stared hastily at his own knees. When Dumbledore spoke, how\-ever, his voice was quite steady.\lang3081\par
