\par
Hagrid\par
\lang3081\i0\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Look at this,\rdblquote  said Harry, handing the note to Hermione.\par
\ldblquote Oh, for heaven\rquote s sake,\rdblquote  she said, scanning it quickly and passing it to Ron, who read it through looking increasingly incredulous.\par
