\lang1033 Harry did not answer. The thought of that little golden bottle had hovered on the edges of his imagination for some time; vague and unformulated plans that involved Ginny splitting up with Dean, and Ron somehow being happy to see her with a new boyfriend, had been fermenting in the depths of his brain, unac\-knowledged except during dreams or the twilight time between sleeping and waking. \'85\lang3081\par
