\lang1033\ldblquote Wha \emdash  ? Yeah, of course,\rdblquote  he said, pulling himself together. \ldblquote Well\lang3081  \lang1033\'85 okay. If I can\rquote t get Slughorn to talk this afternoon, I\rquote ll take some Felix and have another go this evening.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote That\rquote s decided, then,\rdblquote  said Hermione briskly, getting to her feet and performing a graceful pirouette. \ldblquote Destination \'85 determina\-tion \'85 deliberation \'85\rdblquote  she murmured.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Oh, stop that,\rdblquote  Ron begged her, \ldblquote I feel sick enough as it is \emdash  quick, hide me!\rdblquote\lang3081\par
