\lang1033\ldblquote Cool,\rdblquote  said Ron, peering over Hermione\rquote s shoulder to check. \ldblquote Blimey, they don\rquote t look happy, do they?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote They\rquote re the Montgomery sisters and of course they don\rquote t look happy, didn\rquote t you hear what happened to their little brother?\rdblquote  said Hermione.\lang3081\par
