\lang1033\ldblquote Well, their brother was attacked by a werewolf. The rumor is that their mother refused to help the Death Eaters. Anyway, the boy was only five and he died in St. Mungo\rquote s, they couldn\rquote t save him.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
