\lang1033\ldblquote Well, now, this looks absolutely wonderful,\rdblquote  said Slughorn an hour and a half later, clapping his hands together as he stared down into the sunshine yellow contents of Harry\rquote s cauldron. \ldblquote\i Euphoria,\i0  I take it? And what\rquote s that I smell? Mmmm \'85 you\rquote ve added just a sprig of peppermint, haven\rquote t you? Unorthodox, but what a stroke of inspi\-ration, Harry, of course, that would tend to counterbalance the occa\-sional side effects of excessive singing and nose-tweaking. \'85 I really don\rquote t know where you get these brain waves, my boy \'85 unless \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
