\lang1033\ldblquote So, Harry \emdash  you going to use the Felix Felicis or what?\rdblquote  Ron demanded.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, I s\rquote pose I\rquote d better,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote I don\rquote t reckon I\rquote ll need all of it, not twelve hours\rquote  worth, it can\rquote t take all night. \'85 I\rquote ll just take a mouthful. Two or three hours should do it.\rdblquote\lang3081\par
