\lang1033\ldblquote That\rquote s enough!\rdblquote  said Slughorn suddenly, raising a shaking hand. \ldblquote Really, my dear boy, enough \'85 I\rquote m an old man \'85 I don\rquote t need to hear \'85 I don\rquote t want to hear \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
