\lang1033\ldblquote Professor, can you hear me?\rdblquote  he repeated loudly, his voice echo\-ing around the cavern.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Dumbledore panted and then spoke in a voice Harry did not recognize, for he had never heard Dumbledore frightened like this.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote I don\rquote t want\lang3081  \lang1033\'85 Don\rquote t make me \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Harry stared into the whitened face he knew so well, at the crooked nose and half-moon spectacles, and did not know what to do.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote\'85 don\rquote t like \'85 want to stop \'85\rdblquote  moaned Dumbledore.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote You \'85 you can\rquote t stop, Professor,\rdblquote  said Harry. \ldblquote You\rquote ve got to keep drinking, remember? You told me you had to keep drinking. Here \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Hating himself, repulsed by what he was doing, Harry forced the goblet back toward Dumbledore\rquote s mouth and tipped it, so that Dumbledore drank the remainder of the potion inside.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote No \'85\rdblquote  he groaned, as Harry lowered the goblet back into the\lang3081  \lang1033 basin and refilled it for him. \ldblquote I don\rquote t want to. \'85 I don\rquote t want to. \'85 Let me go. \'85\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote It\rquote s all right, Professor,\rdblquote  said Harry, his hand shaking. \ldblquote It\rquote s all right, I\rquote m here \emdash\rdblquote\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Make it stop, make it stop,\rdblquote  moaned Dumbledore.\lang3081\par
\lang1033\ldblquote Yes \'85 yes, this\rquote ll make it stop,\rdblquote  lied Harry. He tipped the con\-tents of the goblet into Dumbledore\rquote s open mouth.\lang3081\par
