\lang1033\ldblquote I\rquote m not coming back even if it does reopen,\rdblquote  said Harry.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 Ron gaped at him, but Hermione said sadly, \ldblquote I knew you were going to say that. But then what will you do?\rdblquote\lang3081\par
