\lang1033\ldblquote Yeah, we shouldn\rquote t miss that,\rdblquote  he said finally.\lang3081\par
\lang1033 His hand closed automatically around the fake Horcrux, but in spite of everything, in spite of the dark and twisting path he saw stretching ahead for himself, in spite of the final meeting with Voldemort he knew must come, whether in a month, in a year, or in ten, he felt his heart lift at the thought that there was still one last golden day of peace left to enjoy with Ron and Hermione.\lang3081\par
